<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>문의 내역 목록</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/common.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/admin/style_check_inquiry.css" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>

  <div class="admin-layout">
    <aside class="admin-sidebar">
      <div class="admin-logo">
        <strong>스마트 약 상자</strong>
        <span>관리자</span>
      </div>

      <nav class="admin-menu">
        <a href="/admin/admin_dashboard/admin">대시보드</a>
        <a href="/admin/admin_dashboard/members">회원관리</a>
        <a href="/admin/admin_dashboard/medicine_boxes">약 상자 관리</a>
        <a href="/admin/admin_dashboard/messages">알림 메시지</a>
        <a href="/admin/check_inquiry" class="active">문의사항 확인</a>
        <a href="/admin/admin_update_announce">공지사항 수정</a>
      </nav>
    </aside>

    <main class="admin-main">
      <header class="admin-header">
        <div>
          <h1>관리자 대시보드</h1>
          <p>스마트 약 상자 서비스 현황을 확인할 수 있습니다.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="admin-user-menu">
          <button type="button" class="admin-user-button" id="adminUserButton">
            관리자
            <span>▼</span>
          </button>

          <div class="admin-user-dropdown" id="adminUserDropdown">
            <a href="/admin/admin_update">개인정보 수정</a>
            <form action="/logout" method="POST" class="logout-form">
              <button type="submit" class="admin-user-item">로그아웃</button>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="inquiry-container">
        <table class="inquiry-table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>유형</th>
              <th>제목</th>
              <th>상태</th>
              <th>작성일</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr onclick="location.href='/admin/answer_inquiry'" style="cursor: pointer;">
              <td>기술문의</td>
              <td class="inquiry-title-cell">스마트 약상자 와이파이 연결이 자꾸 끊어집니다.</td>
              <td><span class="status-badge status-답변완료">답변완료</span></td>
              <td>2026. 07. 02.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr onclick="location.href='/admin/answer_inquiry'" style="cursor: pointer;">
              <td>배송문의</td>
              <td class="inquiry-title-cell">추가 약통 세트 배송 주소를 변경하고 싶습니다.</td>
              <td><span class="status-badge status-답변대기">답변대기</span></td>
              <td>2026. 07. 01.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr onclick="location.href='/admin/answer_inquiry'" style="cursor: pointer;">
              <td>서비스문의</td>
              <td class="inquiry-title-cell">부모님 계정과 제 계정을 연동하는 방법이 궁금합니다.</td>
              <td><span class="status-badge status-답변완료">답변완료</span></td>
              <td>2026. 06. 28.</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>

  <script>
    const adminUserButton = document.getElementById('adminUserButton');
    const adminUserDropdown = document.getElementById('adminUserDropdown');
    adminUserButton.addEventListener('click', () => {
      adminUserDropdown.classList.toggle('show');
    });
    document.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
      if (!adminUserButton.contains(e.target) && !adminUserDropdown.contains(e.target)) {
        adminUserDropdown.classList.remove('show');
      }
    });
  </script>

</body>
</html>